# S06-T07: Installable Mode

## Objective
Surface an in-app install prompt for PWA tablet deployment.

## Acceptance Criteria
- `useInstallPrompt()` captures `beforeinstallprompt` event.
- Top-bar "INSTALL" button shown only when installable + not installed.
- iOS instructions shown for Safari (no native prompt).
- Dismissal persists for 7 days (localStorage).

## Steps
1. Implement `useInstallPrompt` hook.
2. Build `<InstallButton>` per UI_REGULATION ghost-button style.
3. Add Safari instructions modal.
4. Wire dismissal persistence.

## Invariants
- No nag — single button, no popup interrupts.
- Hidden in Tauri build (already installed natively).
- Button styled per UI_REGULATION (cyan ghost, 56×56px touch).
